NG0208:2: de nas yang bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje las /
NG0208:3: gzir dang spogs pa'i drag sngags 'di bton to //
NG0208:4: e ka ya ma bam ram rag mo yam hur thum dzah dun dun trig nan //
NG0208:5: bam bam rngubs ram te shag tsit+ta dgra bo'i srog la hur thum dza /
NG0208:7: snying ga'i snying po sngags bton la //
NG0208:8: ling+ga ming rus brnag pa gzhug / zhag gsum thun brab ro khang mnan //
NG0208:10: rag mo dkar mo'i dkon mo yang spogs par bshad //
NG0208:11: de nas yang bcom ldan 'das kyis 'bras bu gzhom pa'i sbyar ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0208:12: dme thod nang du me long bsag / gser dngul
NG0208:13: zangs lcags rdo nag gzhag / ra dmar nal bu
NG0208:14: khyi nag snying *// steng du gling bzhi rtsibs brgyad dgab //
NG0208:15: de steng srin mo'i sku bzhag la //
NG0208:16: mthing nag dar gyis dgab la bzhag / khrag sna gsum dang dug bsres la //
NG0208:17: ling+ga ming byang g.yag rur gzhug / smyug ma tshigs gsum smin pa la //
NG0208:18: ltas ngan sgro bzhi'i bsgron la bzhag / zhag lnga'i bar du drag sngags bzlas //
NG0208:19: gser de zhu zhing 'phel chad na //
NG0208:20: mda' bcas lcags kyang blugs la dgra la brdeg / srin mo drag tu bskul la 'phang *//
NG0208:21: drag sngags sbyor ba gnyis su bya //
NG0208:22: bam ram kham shig tsit+ta rngubs /
NG0208:23: 'ur tog phrom shar dz+wa la ramsme sha hril /
NG0208:27: ma byung spogs na sngags 'di brdeg / kham tsit+ta
NG0208:28: bam shag rngubs ram phrom hril tog shar dz+wa la
NG0208:29: hur thum ram sma sha b+h+yo /
NG0208:30: srin mo las 'di rgyas par bshad /
NG0208:31: me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:32: lo thog mtha' sdud kyi le'u ste so bdun pa'o ///
NG0208:33: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das kyis las kun
NG0208:34: gyi mtha' sdud du gshin rje bye ba dgu khri'i
NG0208:36: dur khrod gdug pa'i dben gnas su //
NG0208:37: rang sems dben pa'i mtshams bcad la //
NG0208:38: rten rdzas dam rdzas gri bo'i snying *//
NG0208:39: thod pa ri mo bde ldan dar //
NG0208:40: drag po'i hom khung gru gsum la //
NG0208:41: brnag pa'i rten gzugs rgyu rten drug / ba yi lci ba sa dmar la //
NG0208:43: ling+ga sor brgyad dbang po dod //
NG0208:44: nad khrag tsha ba dug chu bsku //
NG0208:45: ri sho dang ni gro ga la //
NG0208:46: de yi ming dang rus bris la //
NG0208:47: snying gar rlan dang sngon dmar bsdam //
NG0208:48: thod par bcug la dong du gzhug / zhing ras
NG0208:49: a mi 'bar gang yang ro ras zhabs ma la
NG0208:50: // sme ba lnga yis thod pa bya //
NG0208:51: gcod pa'i 'khor lo cha gnyis bri //
NG0208:52: dbus nas thig skor bzhi ru bskor //
NG0208:53: dbus su gru gsum zla gam gsum //
NG0208:54: phyi rim 'khrul mig rgya gram ldan //
NG0208:55: yang logs rtsibs mchan bcu gnyis bca' //
NG0208:56: tha ma gdug pa'i ra bas bskor //
NG0208:57: srid pa'i rus sbal lto bar bca' //
NG0208:58: de la gnas pa'i rim pa @#//
NG0208:60: dbus su brnag pa'i snying po gzugs //
NG0208:61: bla gam gsum la srung ba'i lha //
NG0208:62: rgya gram rtsa ba'i drag sngags lus //
NG0208:63: yang logs rtsibs la spu gri rbad //
NG0208:64: gdug pa'i gseb tu mnan pa'i sngags //
NG0208:65: mtshams dang mu ran ming rus khams //
NG0208:66: bkod la tsha ba dug chus bsku //
NG0208:67: thod pa'i steng du 'khor lo bca' //
NG0208:68: drag sngags dmod pa zhag dgur bzlas //
NG0208:69: rang yang zil gnon sku ru gsal //
NG0208:70: bye ba dgu khri'i mdun du bskyed //
NG0208:71: zhing bsnol ru tra'i gdan stengs na //
NG0208:72: chu glang sngon po sbrul ris can //
NG0208:73: thod par nor bus brgyan pa la //
NG0208:74: nyi zla dang bcas gdan la gnas //
NG0208:75: sku mdog sngo nag gtum khro brjid //
NG0208:76: sku stod glang chen stag sham zhing *//
NG0208:77: sbrul dang thod pa rin po ches //
NG0208:78: dbu dang lhu tshigs phyag zhabs brgyan //
NG0208:79: zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir bgrad //
NG0208:80: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NG0208:81: g.yas pa gsum na ral gri dang *//
NG0208:82: be can lcags kyi ri rab bsnams //
NG0208:83: g.yon pa gsum na lcags kyu dang *//
NG0208:84: zhags pa rdo rje rgya gram bsnams //
NG0208:85: zhal nas sbrul dang mi ro 'brul //
NG0208:87: smad nas khrag 'dzag gcan gzan rol //
NG0208:88: thugs dkar nyi ma ya dang sngags //
NG0208:89: dregs pa'i tshul du las la brtson //
NG0208:90: rbad cing drag sngags gtum par bzlas //
NG0208:91: mtha' ru thod pa zhabs 'og gzhug / lcags phur gshin rje'i skur bsgoms la //
NG0208:92: gzir sngags khri yis snying gar gdab //
NG0208:93: pho nyas bkug la rten la bstim //
NG0208:95: rdzas kyi ling+ga phag par gril //
NG0208:96: dar dang re bas thod pa bsdam //
NG0208:97: gnyan sar 'dug pa'i klu la gtad //
NG0208:98: dpang gzug 'o dod cho nges gdab //
NG0208:99: 'byung ba pho brang don yod bsam //
NG0208:100: mnan sngags brgya rtsa brgyad kyis bcag / las kyi kha gso thun dang sbyar //
NG0208:101: drag sngags bstud la lci bar bzlas //
NG0208:102: bla dwags byung na drag sngags brdeg / bla chen
NG0208:103: bzhi la rnal ma brdeg / sprul pa brgyad po
NG0208:104: dbus nas bzlog / yang sprul bcu gnyis mtha' nas
NG0208:105: zlog / chags sdang lnga la 'byung ba dkrug /
NG0208:106: gzir dang mnan la kha gso zor //
NG0208:107: drag sngags spu gri bdun du sbyar //
NG0208:109: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis nyid kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje las drag sngags 'di bton to //
NG0208:110: e ka ya ma hur yam thibs //
NG0208:111: dgra bo srog la bam ril thun dzah yam myags ma ra ya rbad dza dza /
NG0208:112: dun ril bam lam srog la myags ma ra ya rbad /
NG0208:114: tsa dza tsha yang dun ril bam srog la rbad /
NG0208:116: rtsa la dun rbad ma ra ya dza /
NG0208:122: sbyor ba 'di yis ma lus kun //
NG0208:125: 'das kyis las sna tshogs la bskul ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0208:127: bskal pa brgyad khri bzhi stong 'das pa'i pha rol na //
NG0208:128: 'byung ba rten gzhi rngam pa'i 'og shed na //
NG0208:129: rgya mtsho chen po'i gting rum na //
NG0208:130: mun khang lcags mkhar sgo med na //
NG0208:131: ru tra dregs pa'i gdan steng na //
NG0208:132: gshin rje bye ba dgu khri bzhugs //
NG0208:133: sku mdog mthing nag rngam pa la //
NG0208:134: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NG0208:135: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NG0208:136: phyag drug phyag mtshan 'bar ba ni //
NG0208:137: g.yas kyi dang po ral gri 'bar //
NG0208:138: dgra bo'i srog rtsa gcod cing rol //
NG0208:139: g.yas kyi bar ba zhing dbyugs bsnam /
NG0208:140: khams gsum ma lus rdul du rlog / tha ma lcags kyi ri rab bsnams //
NG0208:141: dgra bgegs las ngan gcod cing gzer //
NG0208:142: g.yon gyi dang po be con gyis //
NG0208:143: dgra bo las ngan mgo lus 'joms //
NG0208:144: bar ba lcags kyus dgra snying 'byin //
NG0208:145: tha ma zhags pas dgra bo 'gugs //
NG0208:146: dgra bo las ngan sdig can rnams /
NG0208:147: khyams khang gnas su khrid la shog / sku la lcags kyi tshem tshem gsol //
NG0208:148: zhing dang thod pa sbrul gyis brgyan //
NG0208:149: sku smad stag lpags zhing chung brgyan //
NG0208:150: stod nas nga rgyal me chen 'bar //
NG0208:151: smad nas 'dod chags khrag chen 'brug / sked nas zhe sdang sbrul gyis brgyan //
NG0208:152: zhal nas dug gi rlangs pa 'don //
NG0208:154: snyan nas stong gsum 'brug sgra sgrogs //
NG0208:155: thugs las sprul pa phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NG0208:156: pho nya bye bas dgra bo 'gugs //
NG0208:157: yang sprul dgu khris srog rtsa gcod //
NG0208:158: las kyi mtha' sdud khyod yin gyis //
NG0208:159: dgra bo dam nyams sdig can rnams //
NG0208:160: lag tu gtad do shor ra re //
NG0208:162: 'di la sangs rgyas mi gnas so //
NG0208:163: 'di la dam tshig mi gnas kyis //
NG0208:164: 'di la snying rje'i gnas med kyis //
NG0208:165: rgya mtsho chen po'i gting du sbos //
NG0208:166: lcags kyi ri rab 'og tu non //
NG0208:167: bye ba dgu khri dgu la b+h+yo //
NG0208:168: lcags mkhar btson rar dgra bo chug / dgra bo pho rgyud mo rgyud chod //
NG0208:169: bcol ba'i las rnams 'grub par mdzod //
NG0208:170: bye ba dgu khri sbyor ba bshad //
NG0208:171: me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:172: las kyi mtha' sdud kyi le'u ste so brgyad pa'o ///
NG0208:173: / de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis nyid kyis snying
NG0208:174: gzer nag po bsad pa'i las kyi rim pa bzhi
NG0208:175: ru gsungs pa / kun gyi bcud phyung pa ni /
NG0208:176: gnas rang bzhin gyis dben la nyams dga' ba'i sa ru /
NG0208:177: sems ngang gis dben pa'i mtshams bcad la /
NG0208:178: man+dal khru gang ba'i dbus su //
NG0208:179: dong gru gsum rtse mo lhor bstan pa gcig brtsig de'i nang du thod pa gling mangs sam /
NG0208:180: ling+ga rten dug dang sa dmar la byas pa gnyis
NG0208:181: kyi snying gar ming rus gro ga la bris pa
NG0208:182: gdags / steng du dar nag pos dgab /
NG0208:183: ka pa la gling mang ba'i nang du /
NG0208:185: po'i snying dang bya nag po'i snying dam rdzas su
NG0208:186: bzhag zhag bdun gyi bar du gsal bar byas la
NG0208:187: / bdud kyi rgyal po yab yum dang */
NG0208:188: bdud mi zan ma bcun ma dang nyi ma'i gung la bskul /
NG0208:189: pho nya bdun phrag bdun stong tho rangs bskul /
NG0208:190: bla rkun bdun dang rgyas pa sde bzhi thun bzhir rbad /
NG0208:191: nyung dkar dang nyung nag rdo phye dang khrag skam
NG0208:192: gyi thun brdeg lcags phur bcu bzhi la sngags bcu
NG0208:193: bzlas la ling+ga la thun brdeg / rtsang bdun tshan
NG0208:194: bdun la yang sngags bcu bcu bzlas la brdeg ling+ga
NG0208:195: la snying gzer gyi sngags brgyab pas /
NG0208:197: sprul par bcas pas dgra bo lha srung dang phral nas /
NG0208:198: shes rgyud kyi sgo phye ste /
NG0208:199: snying dkar nag gi mtshams su mtshon cha'i char phab /
NG0208:202: rang rgyud kyi rtsa dang phung po las /
NG0208:205: sha khrag dang rkang rus la rol cing gtor nas /
NG0208:206: bla dang yi ge nr-i rang dbang med par phrogs nas /
NG0208:208: drag sngags 'di nyin mtshan pho mo ma nor bar dag la 'dril zhing rngam par bzlas so //
NG0208:209: go ro shan dgra bo snying gzer yam thun rbad /
NG0208:210: rtsa ro pa na dgra bo snying ram thun rbad /
NG0208:212: dgra bo snying gzer myogs rbad /
NG0208:214: dgra bo snying gzer thum ril rbad /
NG0208:216: dgra bo snying la gzer khas rbad /
NG0208:219: dgra bo snying gzer tsit+ta rbad /
NG0208:220: wa ga sha ling na dgra bo snying gzer nr-i hur thum dza //
NG0208:221: ma ma dgra bo tsit+ta gzer yam thun rbad /
NG0208:222: ma ma rtsa thang dgra bo tsit+ta gzer ram thun rbad /
NG0208:223: ma ma srog rtsa dgra bo tsit+ta gzer myogs rbad /
NG0208:224: ma ma dza la tsit+ta gzer thum ril rbad /
NG0208:225: ma ma srog la dgra bo tsit+ta gzer khas rbad /
NG0208:226: ma ma rtsa thang dgra bo tsit+ta gzer myogs rbad ma ma dgra bo tsit+ta hur thum dzah /
NG0208:227: drag sngags 'od zer rno la myur ba yis /
NG0208:228: shes rgyud rtsa las dwangs snyigs 'byed par 'gyur ro //
NG0208:229: las de thon pa dang ling+ga las phur pa dang rtsang de bton la /
NG0208:230: thod pa dang ling+ga phag pa'i lto bar gril la /
NG0208:231: re ba dang mkhar nag gis bcings te /
NG0208:232: drag sngags pho mos gril la /
NG0208:233: rbad phyung la nan btags te /
NG0208:235: de nas rgya yis bcag dbang chen gyis bsnan /
NG0208:237: ma nyes pa'i dpang gzug snying gzer bsad pa'i kha gso'o //
NG0208:238: de yang dmar len spu gri'i rgyud las //
NG0208:239: bdud dang pho nya sprul pa'i tshogs //
NG0208:240: ma lus rdzogs pa'i las byas nas /
NG0208:241: rtags med brnag pa ma khugs na //
NG0208:242: sbyor ba'i rgyal po dmar len bsngags //
NG0208:243: sems dben gnas su rang mtshams bcad //
NG0208:244: man+dal phur pa hom khung rtsang *//
NG0208:245: ling+ga ming byas sngon dmar gnag / phag gi thod
NG0208:246: par sbubs ma gzhug / rang nyid mi g.yo chos
NG0208:247: sku dang *// phyag rgya chen po zil gnon @#//
NG0208:249: bdud dang pho nya sprul pa mngag / drag sngags
NG0208:250: pho mos nyin mtshan brdeg / brnag pa lha dang
NG0208:251: dpang gzug phral // tsit+ta'i gsang sgor mtshon cha nad //
NG0208:252: phab na rang las bdud gshed slong *//
NG0208:253: dwangs snyigs drag sngags phye dang bla srog sdud //
NG0208:254: sha khrag phung po rol cing za //
NG0208:255: yi ge gnad kyi skabs dang sbyar //
NG0208:256: 'pho ba gsum ni rbad b+h+yo nan //
NG0208:257: drag sngags me rlung las kyi mtshon //
NG0208:258: rang dbang med par srog gcod 'phrog / phu+u la
NG0208:259: ling+ga rtsang bcas brdeg / thod pa gzir zhing thod
NG0208:260: chas gzhug / phag pa sngon dmar re bas gril
NG0208:261: // mnan pa klu dang btsan la gtad //
NG0208:262: la sogs skabs kyis gong dang sbyor /
NG0208:263: kha gso byed pa b+h+yo yis 'phang *//
NG0208:264: gsang ba snying gzer sbyor ba bya //
NG0208:265: nyin mtshan gung dang tho rangs srod //
NG0208:266: dus bzhir rtag tu drag tu bskul //
NG0208:267: mtshon cha sbyor ba'i rgyal por gsungs //
NG0208:269: me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:270: bdud kyi snying gzer nag po'i le'u ste so dgu
NG0208:271: pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis don
NG0208:272: gyi man ngag drag po sngags rgod la /
NG0208:273: gsad gso dbab gcad ltas ngan thog gser las //
NG0208:274: kun 'dus rnam rtog chen po rang la 'byung zhing 'char //
NG0208:275: de yi sbyor ba drag po lnga dang ldan //
NG0208:276: lnga yi mchog tu snying po don gyi las //
NG0208:277: de las 'bru bzhi 'bru brgyad rtsa ba'i sngags //
NG0208:278: 'bru bzhi gsad gso las 'di srung ba'i mchog /
NG0208:279: dwangs ma bzhi yi rtsa las ye shes bzhi shar
NG0208:280: ba / dug lnga las dang sbyor ba gdug pa kun 'joms yin //
NG0208:281: de yi sbyor ba rgyas pa 'di lta ste //
NG0208:282: dur khrod ras sam shog gu gru bzhi la //
NG0208:283: sbyor ba lnga dang tsha ba dug chus sbyang *//
NG0208:284: las kyi 'khor lo mu khyud bzhi ru bskor //
NG0208:285: dbus su gru gsum zla gam gsum dang ldan //
NG0208:286: de yi phyi rim rgya gram rwa bzhir bya //
NG0208:287: yang logs mu khyud zlum po chu yi ris //
NG0208:288: tha mar rtsibs chen bcu gnyis rtse mo nang du bstan /
NG0208:289: srid pa'i khyams khang phag mo'i lto bar bca' //
NG0208:290: de la gnas shing dgod pa'i rim pa ni //
NG0208:291: gru gsum gnod byed snying po ming rnams bri //
NG0208:292: zla gam gsum la stong pa'i ming rnams bri //
NG0208:293: rgya gram rwa bzhir rtsa ba'i 'bru bzhi dgod //
NG0208:294: chu ri mu khyud rbod gtong gdug pa'i ming *//
NG0208:295: bcu gnyis rtsibs la gcod cing gzir ba'i sngags //
NG0208:296: bkod la kha sbyor dar dang sngon dmar bltam //
NG0208:297: thod pa dur mar bcug la gru gsum rtsang bcas rnams //
NG0208:298: phyag rgya zil gnon gsal byas zhag lnga drag tu gzir //
NG0208:299: ling+ga'i snying gar mchog gi phur pa gdab //
NG0208:300: drag tu bskul kyin nad pa du bas bdug / phying pas bkab la nyung dkar brab la bskul //
NG0208:301: las de thon nas bka' rten 'og tu gnan //
NG0208:302: klu dang sa bdag lha yi gdon //
NG0208:303: gshin rje ma mo zhi khro phur pa khyung *//
NG0208:304: dregs pa nyid dang bon po'i rigs gnyis 'dzin //
NG0208:305: bdud dang mu stegs btsan dang @#//
NG0208:307: the'u brang phung bdag rig 'dzin gshin rngog sri can kun //
NG0208:308: rang rang ming dang snying po sbyor ba gcod //
NG0208:309: drag sngags sbyor ba la sogs brgyad dang gsungs //
NG0208:313: srog la breng breng shag dun dun e dam hur
NG0208:314: thum dzahdzahsa na ga snying gzer rbud nan kham shag
NG0208:315: dz+wa la rbad / sa na ga dza /
NG0208:318: sa na ga tsit+ta ro thum rbad /
NG0208:320: sarba sha trum nan 'drid yam bzlog sbur nan /
NG0208:321: e ka ya ma shig 'drid phyung kham shag trig nan /
NG0208:323: sarba sha trum na sha stam+b+ha ya phat rbad /
NG0208:324: 'di bzlas pa'i dus ni rbod gtong nang 'gran pa dang */
NG0208:325: shi kha bye ba dang dmod pa zug pa dang */
NG0208:326: mdze rims drag po me bzhin mched pa dang */
NG0208:329: keg bzlog pa'i dus su bzla'o //
NG0208:330: 'di gar song song bzlas na gdon 'khrug nas god dang glo bur 'ong ngo *//
NG0208:331: me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:332: drag po sngags rgod kyi le'u ste bzhi bcu pa'o
NG0208:333: // // de nas yang bcom ldan 'das kyis srog
NG0208:334: dmar len gyi sbyor ba kun 'byung rtsa ba'i 'khor
NG0208:336: gsang chen mchog tu dril ba yi //
NG0208:337: drag po mngon du phyung ba'i bcud //
NG0208:338: yang gsang sbyor ba lnga gnyis gcig / bde ba smin par byed pa'i sngags //
NG0208:339: ha la nag po'i tsi ma ri //
NG0208:340: dug sbrul nag po 'dzin pa ltar //
NG0208:341: sbyor ba bcu gcig dag dang ldan //
NG0208:342: don gnyis mngon du sbyor ba'i sa //
NG0208:343: bla chen bzhi dang sprul pa brgyad //
NG0208:344: yang sprul bcu gnyis chags sdang 'brel //
NG0208:345: gang byung bsad pa'i sngags bzhi bsdeb //
NG0208:346: rtags med kun 'byung don gnyis sbyar //
NG0208:347: dmar len sngags kyi snying phyung nas //
NG0208:348: las kyi 'khor lo mtshon cha bskor //
NG0208:349: snying po kun gyi mthu dril nas //
NG0208:350: mod la sngags kyi lus dang ming *//
NG0208:351: gsang chen gsang ba'i rgyal por bshad //
NG0208:352: rigs dang rtsol ba las kyi don //
NG0208:354: gang rung drag sngags mtshon char brdeg / rtsa ba'i mtshon cha skabs dang sbyar //
NG0208:355: rtag tu 'byung ba gcig tu dril /
NG0208:356: brgyal bas thig le mthu grol sngags //
NG0208:357: kun 'joms pa yi rgyal por bshad //
NG0208:359: gru bzhir cha mnyam rus sbal ltor //
NG0208:360: ye shes lnga yi thig drangs la //
NG0208:361: de bzhin lho gnyis thig drangs la //
NG0208:362: thig bzhi rgya gram legs btab ste //
NG0208:363: mu khyud rim pa gsum du bskor //
NG0208:364: dbus su gru gsum pho brang der //
NG0208:365: byang khog dbus kyi 'khrul mig gnyis //
NG0208:366: g.yas pa mtshon cha rtsibs bcu la //
NG0208:367: gcig pa'i ral gri bcu dang ldan //
NG0208:368: g.yon pa rgya gram bcu dang ldan //
NG0208:369: drag sngags thun gzir 'bru+u bcu'i gnas //
NG0208:370: rgya gram de bzhin yam yam rngubs //
NG0208:374: gzir dang tsit+ta sbrul gnas pa //
NG0208:375: g.yon gyi rtsibs chen bcu gcig la /
NG0208:376: yam breng dun dun dzah srog 'phrog dgod /
NG0208:377: srid pa'i khyams khang stong na gnas //
NG0208:378: de bzhin srid pa'i 'khrul mig bzhi //
NG0208:379: 'khrul mig ra la mu khyud gsum //
NG0208:380: rtsibs chen bcu gnyis de bzhin bcu //
NG0208:381: cwo lnga rtsibs dang rtsibs bdun la //
NG0208:382: bla chen sprul pa yang sprul dang *//
NG0208:383: chags sdang 'joms pa'i drag sngags te //
NG0208:384: mtshon cha'i rgyal po re la gnas //
NG0208:385: rus spal khog smad lto ba'i rdzing *//
NG0208:386: rin po che yi 'khrul mig bzhir //
NG0208:387: rtsibs bdun rtsibs dgu de bzhin bcu //
NG0208:389: sdeb pa'i drag sngags mtshon re gnas //
NG0208:390: kun gyi lte ba bcu gnyis la //
NG0208:391: rtsa ba'i yi ge 'bru re gnas //
NG0208:392: kun gyi mtha' ru bsreg dang ldan //
NG0208:393: snying po brda ming rus khams sbyar //
NG0208:394: las skabs sbyor ba rig pas gzung *//
NG0208:396: kha sbyar nang na nyi ma'i mchog / dril ba'i mtshon cha sngags bzlas na //
NG0208:397: sbyor ba mchog ni spyod yul rab //
NG0208:398: sngags kyi ngar blud me la bdug / bla bgegs gang byung sngags re gdags //
NG0208:399: kun 'byung rtags med bsnol mar brdeg / dmar len sbyor ba'i rgyal por bshad //
NG0208:400: me rlung sa chu bla chen rtags //
NG0208:401: rta g.yag ba glang ra lugs gshin //
NG0208:402: nya sram sprul pa yin par 'dod //
NG0208:403: sha ba gtsod dang gna' ba bong *//
NG0208:404: wa spyang ri bong byi la dang *//
NG0208:405: phu nu pha tshan zhang drung dang *//
NG0208:406: pha khu la sogs yang sprul rtags /
NG0208:407: khyi phag bya sbrul zhe sdang rtags //
NG0208:408: me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:409: gsang chen mchog sbyor ba'i le'u ste zhe gcig pa'o ///
NG0208:410: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das kyis /
NG0208:411: gsang chen sbyor ba dril ba'i las //
NG0208:412: drag po mngon phyung sbyor ba'i mchog / snying gzer gdug pa thams cad 'joms /
NG0208:414: bdag skyob gzhan srung gdug pa 'joms //
NG0208:415: ma mo bdud pho rgyal po btsan //
NG0208:416: gru[(]tsha glu[)]gnyan sa bdag the brang gri //
NG0208:417: ma lus 'joms pa sgos kyi sngags //
NG0208:418: b+hi li'i khong 'dud khong dregs can //
NG0208:419: 'bar ba nag po ya ma glang *//
NG0208:420: yang gsang mchog gi sbyor ba bshad //
NG0208:421: de yi sbyor ba 'di lta ste //
NG0208:422: dur khrod zhing lpags ro ras la //
NG0208:423: mu khyud lnga ldan rus sbal ltor //
NG0208:424: dug khrag snag tsha sbyar la bri //
NG0208:425: dbus su gru gsum zla gam ldan //
NG0208:426: phyi rim 'khrul mig thod mkhar bzhi //
NG0208:427: de 'og lcags mkhar bang rim brgyad //
NG0208:428: yang logs drag po rtsa sbubs dgu //
NG0208:429: phyi rim mtshon cha bcu drug 'obs //
NG0208:430: srid pa'i rus sbal lto ba ru //
NG0208:432: de la dgod cing gnas pa ni //
NG0208:433: dbus na gdug pa'i snying po ming *//
NG0208:434: zla gam ma mo rgyal po btsan //
NG0208:435: the brang gshin rngog snying po ming *//
NG0208:438: dregs pa stobs kyi 'bru bzhi dgod //
NG0208:439: phyi rim lags mkhar brgyad po la //
NG0208:440: dregs pa stobs kyi 'bru brgyad dgod //
NG0208:441: yang logs drag po rtsa sbubs dgur //
NG0208:442: srog mdangs 'chang ba'i gsang mdzod la //
NG0208:443: snying gzer dgu pa sde tshan re //
NG0208:444: snying po gsum bsdus rdzogs par dgod //
NG0208:445: phyi rim mtshon cha srung ba'i 'obs //
NG0208:446: srid pa'i khang pa bcu drug la //
NG0208:447: shi phrad dgu btul snying po dgod //
NG0208:448: gnyis bcas dug khrag tsha ba bskus /
NG0208:449: kha sbyor sngon dmar mthing nag dril //
NG0208:451: bzlog cing 'byin pa shugs kyi mchog / gcod cing 'bigs pa'i spu gri mtshon //
NG0208:452: bsreg cing g.yengs pas me chu rlung *//
NG0208:453: sdud cing 'chang bas sbyor ba'i mkha' //
NG0208:454: gzir cing gnon pa'i thog ser sa //
NG0208:455: rtsa bar bcas pa'i mtshon lo ma //
NG0208:456: rtsa ba gcig la yan lag stong *//
NG0208:457: bdag skyob gzhan bsrung go mtshon stobs //
NG0208:458: las dang sbyor ba gcod pa'i mtshon //
NG0208:459: 'bar ba nag po zhe sdang mchog / sngags kyi rgyal por dug ngar bcas //
NG0208:460: 'bar ba dug gi dum bur bsdus //
NG0208:461: gdug nag ya ma rag sha'i klong *//
NG0208:462: de yi pho brang thod pa'i gnas //
NG0208:463: dur ma'i phu ru rus sbal gzug / mchod rten rin po che yi sbubs //
NG0208:464: tshangs pa'i bu ga rgya gram e //
NG0208:466: hom shing bcug nas stong stong bzlas //
NG0208:467: gsal bar khyab pa stobs kyis blta //
NG0208:468: rdzas gsum brdab gsum lta ba bzhi //
NG0208:469: 'dus pa gsum dang yin pa bzhi //
NG0208:470: dbang bgrod pa yi go mtshon mchog / rigs la rgyun du stong stong bzlas //
NG0208:471: nya stong sbyor ba btud kyin brtsam //
NG0208:472: drag po thog chen gzer mchog bstan //
NG0208:473: gser gyi dgu thog gnam lcags gzer //
NG0208:474: ri rgyal rbab che spu gri'i dbal //
NG0208:475: yang gsang mchog gi gsang sngags 'di //
NG0208:477: dun dza rag sha rngubs dun /
NG0208:478: sa na ga ma trag shig gzer thum rbad /
NG0208:479: sa na ga du me snying gzer ra thun rbad /
NG0208:480: sa na ga du me snying gzer dug phyung rbad /
NG0208:481: sa na ga snying gzer kham shag rbad /
NG0208:482: sarba u+u na na lam shig gzer thum tsit+ta breng sham hring dza /
NG0208:484: rgyud kyi snying po sbyor ba me rlung gi stobs bsdus pa 'di /
NG0208:485: rang dang bu las gzhan la mi bstan no //
NG0208:486: las gang yang don med na /
NG0208:487: srid pa stobs kyi 'khor lo bcas la /
NG0208:488: snying gzer dgu dang shi phrad kyi sngags stong tsho
NG0208:489: re dang sbyar la lto rjes la sbyor ba drag
NG0208:490: tu byas na gang yang 'grub bo //
NG0208:491: drag sngags brgya brgya rgyun du bzlas so //
NG0208:492: rkyen gang gis kyang mi tshugs so //
NG0208:493: me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:494: shi 'phrad bsrung ba'i le'u ste zhe gnyis pa'o //
NG0208:495: // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis rig sngags sbyor
NG0208:496: ba gdug pa sreg pa'i las spogs pa med par
NG0208:498: dben pa chen po gnyan sa ru //
NG0208:499: gang gnod sa la ma dal bya //
NG0208:502: kha khyer gsum dang ldan pa brtsig / phyi nang chag gang dbus mdzub gang *//
NG0208:503: rtsibs la kha khyer sor gcig bya //
NG0208:504: mu khyud nang du zla gam gsum //
NG0208:505: phyi rim 'khor lo rtsibs bcu gnyis //
NG0208:506: bzhi pa mu khyud zlum po la //
NG0208:507: b+han+d+ha skam rlon bcu gnyis dgod //
NG0208:508: lnga pa me ri'i phreng bas bskor //
NG0208:509: de la dgod pa'i rim pa ni //
NG0208:510: dbus su gru gsum mthing nag la //
NG0208:511: sa chu me rlung sbyor ba'i sbal pa la //
NG0208:512: hom shing khru gang gru gsum brtsig kha khyer gsum dang zla gam la //
NG0208:513: gdug pa gsum gyi gzugs brnyan gzhag / rtsibs la rtsa ba'i drag sngags dgod //
NG0208:514: phyi rim mtshon cha'i rtse mo la //
NG0208:515: bsreg cing gnon pa'i spu gri dgod //
NG0208:516: mu khyud bzhi pa'i 'khor lo b+han+d+ha la yang la //
NG0208:517: sbal pa sbrul dang nya sram sha / gnyis pa sha chen tsha ba gsum //
NG0208:518: bzhi pa dug gi ri lu brgya //
NG0208:519: lnga pa bya phag spyang tshil gsum //
NG0208:520: drug pa mi rta khyi yi tshil //
NG0208:521: bdun pa mar khu dug chu brgyad //
NG0208:522: dgu pa khrag sna chang sna bcu //
NG0208:523: bcu gcig dug rdzas sna tshogs bzhag / dur khrod ras sam zhing ras la //
NG0208:524: gong bzhin bris la rdzas kyis bskus //
NG0208:525: bdun nam dgu ru steng nas dgab //
NG0208:526: dmod pa bzlas shing bskong ba bya //
NG0208:527: drag tu bskul zhing me sbar la //
NG0208:528: gzugs la mtshon brdag[(]tsha brdeg[)]gdab la bsreg / gdug pa'i sha sogs rim gyis dbul //
NG0208:529: them nas rjes shul brnag pa'i zor //
NG0208:530: nyin mtshan thun drug sbyin bsreg bya //
NG0208:531: drag po sbyor ba mchog gi las //
NG0208:532: ho ban nya yi bde klong du //
NG0208:533: snying po gsum la dbang du sdud //
NG0208:534: man ngan gnad mda'i sbyor bas bsreg / las sbyor nus pa dam du 'brel //
NG0208:535: phyag rgya chen po'i lus dbang srun //
NG0208:536: bde ba'i don du rang las 'char //
NG0208:537: gdug pa rjes gcod sngags kyi dbal //
NG0208:538: bag med sbyor ba kun 'joms yin //
NG0208:539: rnal 'byor can las gzhan du min //
NG0208:540: mdze rims dag po'i yams dar na //
NG0208:541: sbyor ba'i rgyal po bstud la brtsam //
NG0208:543: sa na ga u nan gzer phyung *//
NG0208:544: srog dun ram tsi ta breng shag rbad hur thum myogs rbad /
NG0208:545: drag po mngon du phyung ba'i sbyor ba 'di ni /
NG0208:546: las gang gi rtags ma phyin na /
NG0208:547: khyad par dang rdzas dang bca' thabs 'phrul par byas la /
NG0208:548: sngags pa go mtshon gnyis dang ldan par byas te /
NG0208:549: khro bo'idaka' thub dang dam tshig bsrung la las brtsams na 'bras bu re dogs med pa'o //
NG0208:550: me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:551: drag po mngon du phyung ba'i sbyor ba'i le'u ste
NG0208:552: zhe gsum pa'o // // de nas yang bcom ldan
NG0208:553: 'das kyis / kha gso'i dus su nya dang stong
NG0208:554: dang tshes brgyad dang nyi shu bzhi la mon thod
NG0208:555: 'das kyis / dam / 'brong gi ru g.yas pa
NG0208:556: rtse mo ma bcad pa'i nang du khrag sna dang
NG0208:557: dug sna dang ling+ga dang ming rus bcug la phur
NG0208:558: 'das kyis / dam / bus gdab / gri yis gtubs zor du bstim /
NG0208:561: e myags ya rngubs mug shag ka dun dgra bo'i srog la thum ril b+h+yo /
NG0208:562: las de dag la rtags med na /
NG0208:565: zhag gsum du rnal ma dang sngags bzlog mar brdeg mnan pa dang kha gso 'dra'o //
NG0208:566: las gang yang rtags med dam stobs chen nang rgyas drag po sngags kyi 'byung ba dkrug par /
NG0208:567: thod pa dang 'khor lo la dug shing gi dud pas bdug kho'i srung ma gzir /
NG0208:570: sngags kyi dug mda' khong du bskyal /
NG0208:573: gsang ba man ngag tu lto sdeb pa ni /
NG0208:574: e myags ya rngubs mug shag ka dun snying gzer sbur nan /
NG0208:575: la tsa la tsa ma ri phyung */
NG0208:578: e myags ya rngubs mug shag ka dun dgra bo'i srog la thum ri li li b+h+yo /
NG0208:579: e myags ya rngubs mug shag 'di la man ngag byed pa'i bsad pa'i spu gri bsdebs pas /
NG0208:580: man ngag gsang ba'i sdebs gsum mo //
NG0208:581: me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:582: kha gso ba'i le'u ste zhe bzhi pa'o //    // de nas yang bcom ldan 'das kyis /
NG0208:583: khro bo mngon du mthong ba'i don 'di gsungs so //
NG0208:584: dpal chen pos sngon gdug pa can btul nas bstan pa /
NG0208:585: e badzra kro ta ma ha shri he ru ka tri dzahdzahdzah rak+sha thum ril rbad /
NG0208:586: rdzogs par bskyed cing tshogs mchod bya //
NG0208:587: drag por bzlas shing rngam g.yab btang *//
NG0208:588: 'jig rten gdon rnams rdul du rlog / sngon byung rjes 'jug phrin las da lta rdzogs //
NG0208:589: drag thabs 'di yis khro bo mngon du mthong *//
NG0208:591: 'jig rten zil gyi gnon pa'i me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:592: mngon du mthong ba'i le'u ste zhe lnga pa'o //    // de nas yang 'jigs byed chen po des //
NG0208:593: zhi bas dug lnga sbyangs te bsad pa'i don 'di gsungs so //
NG0208:594: zhi ba'i las rnams bsgrub pa ni //
NG0208:595: gang yin gzas pa'i ming rus dang */
NG0208:596: rdzas dang dug mda' 'phrog pho mo gnyis bsdom srog snying la gnod byed thum ril b+h+yo /
NG0208:597: zhi ba shan+tim ku ru swa ha /
NG0208:599: 'jig rten zil gyi gnod pa'i me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:600: zhi ba'i las kyi bsad pa'i le'u ste zhe drug pa'o ///
NG0208:601: / de nas yang 'jigs byed chen po des /
NG0208:602: nag po mthar byed klu'i don 'di gsungs so //
NG0208:603: nag po mthar byed man ngag la //
NG0208:604: klu yi dmod pas thebs pa la /
NG0208:607: gu gul dud pas bdug pa'o //
NG0208:608: mdze mo'i gos la ling+ga bca' //
NG0208:609: sbal gzugs brgyad dang ming gzugs brgyad //
NG0208:610: pha mes thod pa yod na rab //
NG0208:611: med na rabs chad thod pa la //
NG0208:612: nang du ling+ga re bas gril la gzhug / ngan thod de dang kha sbyar nas //
NG0208:615: de 'dra'i drag sngags bzlas pa ni //
NG0208:618: dzahdzah ma ma trag hu ya hu ya /
NG0208:619: nr-i rbad na ga bam bu /
NG0208:621: he he dum bu+u dum rbud /
NG0208:622: hu ya hu ya na ga na rbad rbad /
NG0208:623: na ga klu'i gnod pa la gdon mi za'o //
NG0208:626: na ga mthar byed kyi le'u ste zhe bdun pa'o
NG0208:627: // // de nas yang 'jigs byed chen po des
NG0208:628: / rgyal po'i smyo 'bog bsad pa'i las 'di gsungs so //
NG0208:629: seng ge'i thod pa dug dang khrag gis byug /
NG0208:630: ling+ga ming rus bcas pa gzhug / shel gyi phur
NG0208:631: pa nas tsam brdeg / thun brdeg dgra yi 'gram
NG0208:632: par mnan // de yi drag sngags 'di lta ste //
NG0208:633: e snying rtsa breng breng hur myogs sa ma ya thibs thum snying rtsa hur nan /
NG0208:635: 'jig rten zil gyis mnan pa'i me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las //
NG0208:636: ra tsa smyo 'bog gi le'u ste zhe brgyad pa'o
NG0208:637: // // de nas yang 'jigs byed chen po des
NG0208:638: / drag po'i rdzas kyi man ngag la //
NG0208:639: thig le bzhi la 'khar phor du //
NG0208:640: seng ge'i 'o ma bzhos pa dang *//
NG0208:641: phra men nag po sna tshogs dang *//
NG0208:642: bse zho sbal pa'i rgyu las /
NG0208:643: rtsangs pa'i khrag dang de rnams blug / thig le
NG0208:644: chen po dang rta yung dug chen pos brgyan byas
NG0208:645: te / des ni sbyor ba the tshom med //
NG0208:648: 'jig rten zil gyis gnon pa'i me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:649: drag po rdzas kyi le'u ste zhe dgu pa'o ///
NG0208:650: / de nas 'jigs byed chen po des /
NG0208:651: mu stegs rngu brag 'don pa'i don 'di gsungs so //
NG0208:652: dri ma rkang rjes sa dag las //
NG0208:653: nyung dkar nyung nag skye tshe la /
NG0208:654: khrag sna gsum la 'phang la gtad //
NG0208:656: de nas yang rdzas sngags 'di bton to //
NG0208:657: e snying khrag la phri phri nan /
NG0208:660: thum gung a ro la rbad /
NG0208:662: yid gnyis the tshom med pa las //
NG0208:663: drag po mu stegs ngan sngags yin //
NG0208:664: thams cad dbang du sdud pa yin //
NG0208:666: 'jig rten zil gyis gnon pa'i me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:667: mu stegs ngan sngags kyi le'u ste lnga bcu tham pa'o ///
NG0208:668: / de nas yang 'jigs byed chen po des /
NG0208:669: gnod sbyin srog gi gseg brdar gyi don 'di gsungs so //
NG0208:670: thams cad dbang du sdud pa yin /
NG0208:671: a la tha la phru ba rbad /
NG0208:672: tang bum ze ma ni rbad /
NG0208:674: ro ras la dgra bo'i ming bris la /
NG0208:675: sus kyang ma mthong sa ru bzlas //
NG0208:676: ling+ga rabs chad thod par gzhug / mi yi lag ngar tho bas brdung *//
NG0208:678: 'jig rten zil gyi gnon pa'i me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:679: gnod sbyin srog gi gsog brdar gyi le'u ste nga gcig pa'o ///
NG0208:681: nas yang 'jigs byed chen po des /
NG0208:682: btsan drag gzer gyi drag sngags 'di gsungs so //
NG0208:683: dri ma drug la ling+ga bya /
NG0208:684: khrag sna dug sna dag gis byug / ming rus
NG0208:685: thod pa'i nang du bcug / gri lcags phur bu
NG0208:686: sor bzhi gdab // gong gsum btsan la gnan pa bya //
NG0208:687: de yi drag sngags 'di lta ste //
NG0208:688: e ma rag ya rag sha dgra snying pa la rbad rbad thum thum /
NG0208:689: drag sngags brgyad khri bzhi stong du bzlas /
NG0208:690: 'bum du bzlas pas the tshom med //
NG0208:692: 'jig rten zil gyis gnon pa'i me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:693: btsan drag gzer gyi le'u ste nga gnyis pa'o //
NG0208:694: // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis don gnyis sngon
NG0208:696: tshad ma bzhi yis rab bstan pa'i //
NG0208:697: don gyi dgongs pa bsdus pa 'di //
NG0208:698: rtsol dang bsgrub pa'i mtha' las 'das //
NG0208:700: rgyu rkyen bgrod pa'i sar ma lhung *//
NG0208:701: rdzas dang rtags la rten mi 'cha' /
NG0208:702: mchod dang thugs dam bskang mi dgos //
NG0208:703: thams cad ngo bo ma bcos pa'o /
NG0208:704: kho na chos nyid gcig pa la //
NG0208:705: lhun grub rang byung longs spyod sku //
NG0208:706: las dang sbyor ba sna tshogs sprul //
NG0208:707: sku gsum ma btsal bgrod thob med //
NG0208:708: 'di dag chos nyid rol pa'i rgya //
NG0208:709: chos nyid bde ba rang byung dpal //
NG0208:710: ye shes chen po rang gsal ba //
NG0208:713: ngo bo mi dmigs gnyis kyis dben //
NG0208:714: snang stong gnyis med ye shes sku //
NG0208:715: 'dzin rtog mtha' bzhi rang bzhin med //
NG0208:716: med pa'i ngang las snying po gnas //
NG0208:717: sgyu ma lhun grub yul la rol //
NG0208:718: 'khor ba ma spangs rang sar yal //
NG0208:719: gsal ba de nyid lhun gyis grub //
NG0208:720: 'bras bu btsal med bde bar gnas //
NG0208:721: bdag nyid chen po ye rdzogs pa'o //
NG0208:723: phrin las ma btsal lhun gyis rdzogs //
NG0208:724: sangs rgyas gsung gi zab mor gnas //
NG0208:725: bgrod pa dbang gi phyag rgyas btab //
NG0208:726: rdo rje stong bdag che bar gnas //
NG0208:727: sangs rgyas sems can ma lus kun //
NG0208:728: rgyud 'di bzung zhing gnas par bya //
NG0208:729: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa las /
NG0208:730: 'khor thams cad yi rang ste mngon par bstod do //
NG0208:731: dpal tshe bdag gi me rlung skye 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:732: 'khor la gtad pa'i le'u ste nga gsum pa'o //
NG0208:733: // rgyud kyi yang snying dam pa zhes bya ba'i
NG0208:735: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dmod pa bsgral ba /
NG0208:736: lha yul du grags pa me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs
NG0208:737: pa'i rgyud ces bya ba rdzogs so // rgyud 'di
NG0208:738: dpe sdur sa yang ma rnyed cing yig nor rgyun
NG0208:739: 'byams mang yang dpe rgyun chad pa las drag snyam
